WEBVTT

00:00:10.997 --> 00:00:14.923
TAPE THREE WITH MISTER WACLAW JABLONSKI.

00:00:14.608 --> 00:00:15.327
YEA.

00:00:16.431 --> 00:00:18.922
vi lang hostu geven in AUSCHWITZ?

00:00:19.755 --> 00:00:21.082
zog ikh dokh dir.

00:00:21.612 --> 00:00:25.149
in Aushvits bin ikh gevezn akht monatn.

00:00:26.235 --> 00:00:28.831
un in Bukhnvald bin ikh gevezn

00:00:28.831 --> 00:00:30.347
tsvey yor.

00:00:30.943 --> 00:00:32.709
dos, du gedenkst

00:00:33.340 --> 00:00:37.518
oys- oysergeveyntlekhe geshenung

00:00:37.525 --> 00:00:39.949
vos iz geshen in AUSCHWITZ?

00:00:40.512 --> 00:00:43.628
neyn, ikh, vayl ikh bin avek fun Aushvits.

00:00:43.262 --> 00:00:44.741
in zeks monatn?

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:47.570
yo, UNK a por gesheenishn,

00:00:47.570 --> 00:00:50.765
di same vikhtikn gesheenishn, m'hot gehat

00:00:51.042 --> 00:00:54.647
a kolnidre geheym in AUSCHWITZ.

00:00:54.670 --> 00:00:56.604
dos iz di sensatsye.

00:00:57.319 --> 00:00:59.743
un an andere zakh vos iz geshen?

00:00:58.905 --> 00:01:02.918
yo, untererdishe bavegung, geholfn, getun,

00:01:02.918 --> 00:01:04.805
keyn badoytung nisht.

00:01:04.677 --> 00:01:07.438
vos hostu gemakht mit untererdishe?

00:01:08.372 --> 00:01:13.614
oh! m'hot, di vikhtikste zakh vos m'hot gemakht vel ikh dir zogn,

00:01:13.654 --> 00:01:14.812
farshrayb!

00:01:16.523 --> 00:01:20.417
in Aushvits hobn zikh di heftlingen, di arestantn

00:01:20.417 --> 00:01:22.726
kegnzaytik gemordet.

00:01:24.403 --> 00:01:30.168
polyakn hobn gemordet tshekhn, tshekhn hobn gemordet polyakn, yidn azoy vayter.

00:01:31.153 --> 00:01:33.850
in Aushvits iz geven shreklekh!

00:01:33.850 --> 00:01:36.736
khuts dem vos di natsis hobn gemordet,

00:01:36.736 --> 00:01:40.313
hobn di farshidene natsyonalitetn zikh gemordet.

00:01:40.313 --> 00:01:43.114
un mir hobn gefirt an arbet

00:01:43.114 --> 00:01:46.182
oyfhern zikh kegnzaytik mordn.

00:01:48.349 --> 00:01:53.304
un m'hot opgeshtelt dem felker-mord in Aushvits.

00:01:53.547 --> 00:01:55.481
un m'hot ongehoybn

00:01:55.639 --> 00:01:58.687
helfn eyner dem andern.

00:01:59.672 --> 00:02:01.404
shtel dikh for,

00:02:01.883 --> 00:02:09.035
m'hot aykh, di polyakn hobn afile geholfn yidn aroysfirn fun Aushvits, rateven zey,

00:02:09.035 --> 00:02:10.433
do iz do a yid

00:02:10.437 --> 00:02:12.494
velkher iz gevorn opgeratevet

00:02:12.494 --> 00:02:13.807
a dank zey.

00:02:14.370 --> 00:02:16.119
vi az zey hobn gemakht?

00:02:16.547 --> 00:02:25.400
dos hey- o dos iz es. zey hobn gehat di farbindung mit di oyserlekhe zayt, bay nakht, geganvet, gegrob- oysergeveyntlekhe vegn.

00:02:26.622 --> 00:02:29.940
mentshn zenen gegangen oyf arbet, antlofn, geratevet,

00:02:30.351 --> 00:02:34.665
mir hobn afile do, zog ikh dir, eyn yid velkher iz gevorn geratevet durkh

00:02:34.823 --> 00:02:37.534
ffun di polyakn in Aushvits.

00:02:37.000 --> 00:02:41.736
un du hot nisht ge- gemakh- geratevet, du?

00:02:40.932 --> 00:02:42.017
ikh nisht.

00:02:42.017 --> 00:02:44.959
mikh hot men avekgefirt fun Aushvits keyn Bukhnvald.

00:02:44.610 --> 00:02:49.036
BUT frier, s'hot nisht keyn POSSIBLITY tsu avek,

00:02:48.947 --> 00:02:54.729
m'hot, zog ikh dir, m'hot gefirt a kamf oyftsuhern zikh kegnzaytik mordn.

00:02:55.849 --> 00:03:00.500
di heftlingen, di rusn, tshekhn, polyakn,

00:03:01.435 --> 00:03:03.018
andere felker,

00:03:03.018 --> 00:03:05.984
hobn zikh nisht fartrogn, di daytshn hobn gehetst

00:03:06.193 --> 00:03:08.650
un m'hot zikh kegnzaytik gemordet.

00:03:09.282 --> 00:03:11.785
un mir hobn gefirt an arbet

00:03:11.785 --> 00:03:15.638
oyfhern zikh mordn di heftlingen, di arestantn.

00:03:16.588 --> 00:03:19.248
zog ikh dir, geb ikh dir dem bayshpil,

00:03:20.217 --> 00:03:24.500
az m'hot afile geholfn, di polyakn hobn geholfn a yid,

00:03:24.500 --> 00:03:26.791
aroyskrign fun Aushvits,

00:03:27.355 --> 00:03:32.023
m'hot im avekgefirt keyn Kroke, er iz geblibn lebn, un er lebt nokh, er iz nokh do.

00:03:32.215 --> 00:03:33.947
vi heyst er dortn?

00:03:35.607 --> 00:03:37.575
Shimen Zaydof, yo?

00:03:38.087 --> 00:03:39.718
Shimon Zaydof.

00:03:41.142 --> 00:03:45.354
ven du host avekgeganen fun Aushvits, d-

00:03:46.288 --> 00:03:48.445
vos iz geshen in a-

00:03:48.445 --> 00:03:53.673
tsu nemen dir tsu Bukhnvald? vos iz geshen? far vos hostu ge- avekgeganen?

00:03:53.460 --> 00:04:08.304
dos iz gevezn in dray un fertsikstn yor, di daytshn hobn zikh shoyn gefinen in a shvere militerishe lage, hot men genumen farshidene arbeter fun Aushvits, avekgefirt keyn Bukhnvald, keyn Daytshland.

00:04:09.694 --> 00:04:14.548
mikh hot men arayngeshtupt in a shnayder-varshtat ver hot gearbet far di daytshn.

00:04:14.470 --> 00:04:18.008
du host gevolt geyn, ober zey hobn dir gezogt az?

00:04:16.478 --> 00:04:19.054
zey dets- zey hobn detsidirt.

00:04:19.887 --> 00:04:21.045
farshteyst?

00:04:21.135 --> 00:04:25.381
s'geven a an apel vos m'hot gezogt az m'geyt?

00:04:25.759 --> 00:04:27.224
zey shteln dort

00:04:27.224 --> 00:04:29.955
zey hobn oysgerufn nemen, fakhn,

00:04:29.961 --> 00:04:31.372
bloyz fakhlayt,

00:04:31.581 --> 00:04:34.877
shnayder, shusters, stolyers, farshidene,

00:04:34.877 --> 00:04:39.034
ir geyt keyn Bukhnvald, nu vos zol ikh zogn? konst dokh nisht zogn neyn.

00:04:39.428 --> 00:04:40.671
bist gegangen.

00:04:40.390 --> 00:04:41.902
ven hot dos geven?

00:04:42.330 --> 00:04:45.547
in dray un fertsikstn yor in april.

00:04:48.321 --> 00:04:53.647
un vos iz gesh- vi hostu geganen tsu Bukhnvald, oyfn ban oyfn?

00:04:52.692 --> 00:04:56.601
m'hot di banen avekgefirt keyn Vaymar,

00:04:57.197 --> 00:05:01.730
un fun Vaymar hot men undz gefirt keyn Bukhnvald,

00:05:02.192 --> 00:05:03.842
dos iz an ort

00:05:03.842 --> 00:05:05.766
vi Gete hot gelebt.

00:05:05.766 --> 00:05:08.126
veyst der daytsh, der barimter

00:05:09.145 --> 00:05:13.656
un fun Vaymar dortn keyn Bukhnvald iz men gegangen tsu fus,

00:05:13.656 --> 00:05:16.850
vayl s'geven akht kilometer.

00:05:18.342 --> 00:05:25.373
arayngekumen keyn Bukhnvald, yeder eyner hot gekrign an ort in lager un m'arbet un azoy vayter un azoy vayter.

00:05:25.075 --> 00:05:26.759
et hot gekrign a nomen?

00:05:26.644 --> 00:05:27.549
vos?

00:05:27.881 --> 00:05:28.916
A NUMBER?

00:05:28.770 --> 00:05:29.979
avade!

00:05:30.357 --> 00:05:33.371
ikh bin dokh geven a polyak, nisht keyn yid,

00:05:33.462 --> 00:05:38.012
un ikh hob gekrign dem NUMBER elef toyznt fir hundert finef.

00:05:38.406 --> 00:05:41.268
un vu hostu es ongeshribn, oyfn?

00:05:40.752 --> 00:05:46.669
do iz geven a tseykhn, opgedrukt, aroyf geshribn, elef toyznt fir hundert finef,

00:05:47.586 --> 00:05:50.764
zey iz nisht gegangen keyn nemen, der nu- der numer,

00:05:50.764 --> 00:05:52.440
ot dos hot detsidirt.

00:05:52.328 --> 00:05:55.258
in Aushvits oykhet du hot ge-

00:05:53.948 --> 00:05:55.528
in Aushvits oykhet.

00:05:55.348 --> 00:05:56.540
di zelbe?

00:05:55.551 --> 00:05:56.872
ikh yo.

00:05:56.872 --> 00:05:59.763
yidn hot men oyfgeshribn in der hant do.

00:05:59.972 --> 00:06:05.653
vi hostu gekrign di papirn vos hot gezogt az du bist nisht a yid, du bist yetst a polyak?

00:06:04.596 --> 00:06:11.154
hob ikh dokh dir gezogt, bakante ho'mir nokh aroysgegebn far dem eyder ikh bin gevorn arestirt.

00:06:12.966 --> 00:06:14.681
hob ikh dir dertseylt shoyn.

00:06:15.430 --> 00:06:16.807
host shoyn fartseykhnt.

00:06:17.877 --> 00:06:29.295
un eyner iz geshtorbn un azoy vayter, hot er avekgegebn dokument, un ikh bin shoyn geven oyf di arishe zayt mit dem dokument. un der dokument bin ikh geven in Pavyak, un der dokument bin ikh geven in Bukhnvald,

00:06:29.301 --> 00:06:34.222
aroys, nokh di milkhome oykh geblibn bay dem dokument, Yabloynske.

00:06:34.887 --> 00:06:35.792
shoyn.

00:06:36.034 --> 00:06:39.364
un vest ven du host ongekumen tsu Bukhnvald,

00:06:39.364 --> 00:06:40.854
mit a sakh mentshn?

00:06:41.080 --> 00:06:43.397
toyznt mentshn zenen gekumen.

00:06:43.397 --> 00:06:47.081
fun Aushvits keyn Bukhnvald toyznt mentshn.

00:06:46.446 --> 00:06:48.662
vi lang host gen- genum-

00:06:48.662 --> 00:06:51.368
biz Aushvits a Bukhnvald?

00:06:51.373 --> 00:06:53.156
vifl kilometer?

00:06:52.369 --> 00:06:56.193
vi lang host bay ban, oyfn fu-

00:06:55.137 --> 00:06:58.995
dos hot lang nisht lang gedoyert, dray teg, shoyn.

00:06:59.895 --> 00:07:02.285
dray teg iz men shoyn gevezn

00:07:02.443 --> 00:07:04.951
fun Aushvits in Vaymar.

00:07:04.536 --> 00:07:08.006
zey hot gegebn geesn oyfn veg?

00:07:07.438 --> 00:07:09.626
yo, epes mitgegebn.

00:07:10.324 --> 00:07:17.625
s'geve- ale mentshn vos hobn ge- oysgegangen fun Aushvits hot gekumen tsu Bukhnvald? Ale.

00:07:16.483 --> 00:07:17.189
yo.

00:07:17.189 --> 00:07:20.342
toyznt mentshn, ale zenen gekumen keyn Bukhnvald.

00:07:20.213 --> 00:07:23.379
un vos iz geshen ves- ven du host gekumen tsu Bukhnvald?

00:07:23.622 --> 00:07:24.817
nu shoyn.

00:07:24.817 --> 00:07:27.294
zey m'hot undz registrirt,

00:07:28.684 --> 00:07:32.896
yeder eyner hot gekrign an ort vu tsu nekhtikn, vu tsu voynen,

00:07:33.510 --> 00:07:35.411
un gekrign arbet.

00:07:35.586 --> 00:07:42.735
vos far a fakh, eyner a shuster, a shnayder, a mekhanik, a tekhnik, vayl in Bukhnvald iz gevezn

00:07:43.483 --> 00:07:46.784
a groyse amunitsye fabrik

00:07:47.905 --> 00:07:51.493
velkhe hot geheysn Guslov-Verke.

00:07:52.967 --> 00:07:59.930
un dortn hot men badorfn farshidene fakhlayt zoln oysarbetn gever far der daytsher armey.

00:08:01.371 --> 00:08:07.544
ven du host gekumen arayn in Bukhnvald hobn zey gemakht di hor, di?

00:08:07.412 --> 00:08:09.009
ne dos.

00:08:07.544 --> 00:08:10.680
neyn? gornisht. in Aushvits?

00:08:10.129 --> 00:08:12.840
in Aushvits, yo, oder do nisht.

00:08:11.496 --> 00:08:12.469
yo.

00:08:13.251 --> 00:08:16.519
do iz geven besere badingungen in Bukhnvald.

00:08:16.947 --> 00:08:18.139
geven beser.

00:08:19.917 --> 00:08:22.644
un vi lang hostu geven dortn

00:08:22.920 --> 00:08:25.749
far du host geganen tsun arbet?

00:08:27.223 --> 00:08:30.524
bald gegangen tsu der arbet in shnayderay,

00:08:32.100 --> 00:08:37.173
un biz tsu der bafrayung, tsvishn tsayt hot men mikh avekgeshikt, do dortn,

00:08:37.399 --> 00:08:39.738
di bafrayung iz gekumen

00:08:39.897 --> 00:08:42.827
dem eleftn april,

00:08:42.985 --> 00:08:46.269
toyznt nayn hundert finef un fertsik.

00:08:48.030 --> 00:08:51.655
vos hostu getun ale tog? host host gemakht

00:08:51.655 --> 00:08:54.909
vos hostu gemakht ven du du host gemakht a shnayder?

00:08:53.903 --> 00:08:55.550
shnayderay.

00:08:55.050 --> 00:08:56.782
ye vos hostu gemakht?

00:08:56.653 --> 00:09:01.102
hoyzn, bluzes, militerishe ontuekhtser.

00:09:01.378 --> 00:09:02.570
far vemenen?

00:09:03.505 --> 00:09:05.136
far di armeyen.

00:09:05.428 --> 00:09:06.957
far di S. S.

00:09:07.133 --> 00:09:13.303
du host gearbet bloyz in Bukhnvald, oder du s- host avekgeganen in andere andere erter?

00:09:10.812 --> 00:09:13.303
in Bukhnvald, in Bukhnvald.

00:09:14.305 --> 00:09:18.754
shpeter hob ikh gearbet dortn an oysern komande a tsayt, dos iz nisht vikhtik.

00:09:18.878 --> 00:09:20.002
Bukhnvald.

00:09:20.025 --> 00:09:25.031
BUT du host gearbet in a in a kleyn shto- sh- shtetl,

00:09:23.957 --> 00:09:25.014
vos?

00:09:25.290 --> 00:09:26.178
vos?

00:09:25.307 --> 00:09:26.955
host gearbet,

00:09:26.455 --> 00:09:27.208
yo.

00:09:27.012 --> 00:09:28.831
in an andere shtetl.

00:09:28.831 --> 00:09:31.157
f- makhn di UNIFORMS.

00:09:30.707 --> 00:09:35.054
shpeter hot men mikh avekgeshikt oyf etlekhene monatn keyn Arolzn.

00:09:36.934 --> 00:09:40.635
dortn hob ikh gearbet oykh in a shnayder varshtat.

00:09:40.635 --> 00:09:47.778
nakher hot men tsurikgebrengt mikh, vayl m'hot drotn punkt badorfn hobn mentshn hot men mir geshikt dortn keyn Arolzn.

00:09:47.228 --> 00:09:49.095
vi lang hostu geven dortn?

00:09:49.033 --> 00:09:52.402
a p= dray monatn, tsi fir monatn in Arolzn.

00:09:52.527 --> 00:09:54.866
un du host gearbet in andere erter?

00:09:54.838 --> 00:09:56.396
shoyn mer nisht.

00:09:56.396 --> 00:09:58.376
Bukhnvald, Arolzn.

00:10:01.065 --> 00:10:04.687
un vu hostu gevoynt ven du host geven in Arolzn?

00:10:05.470 --> 00:10:11.556
dortn iz geven ge- spetsyele erter far heftlingen, far arestantn.

00:10:12.507 --> 00:10:18.646
arop gegebn dortn aza shtik plats un azoy vayter, vayl dortn hot zikh gefinen a shule,

00:10:18.646 --> 00:10:21.461
a militerishe ofitsir shule,

00:10:21.484 --> 00:10:27.485
un m'hot far zey gearbet un azoy vayter, un mir hobn gevoynt do in a hayzl.

00:10:27.930 --> 00:10:33.071
un du host gemakht untererdishe zakhn ven du host geven in Bukhnvald?

00:10:33.700 --> 00:10:34.430
yo.

00:10:35.895 --> 00:10:38.116
vos zakhn?

00:10:38.427 --> 00:10:39.923
vos heyst vos zakhn?

00:10:39.405 --> 00:10:42.149
vos du ho- vos hostu gemakht ven?

00:10:41.565 --> 00:10:42.369
her, o!

00:10:43.168 --> 00:10:46.202
in Bukhnvald, di bavegung hot ge-

00:10:46.202 --> 00:10:48.276
hot gefirt an arbet

00:10:48.518 --> 00:10:52.545
a por yidishe, kegnzaytik zikh helfn,

00:10:52.838 --> 00:11:01.134
oyb emetser iz geven badrot hot men im bahaltn, m'hot getun vikhtike, politishe, gezelshaftlekhe arbetn.

00:11:01.562 --> 00:11:02.872
in Bukhnvald,

00:11:01.562 --> 00:11:03.378
azoy vi vos vos?

00:11:03.688 --> 00:11:05.676
veyst nisht vos s'taytsh keyn verter?

00:11:05.676 --> 00:11:09.049
m'hot genumen, az eyner UNK iz geven badrot,

00:11:09.477 --> 00:11:13.588
hot men arayngefirt in shpitol arayn, m'hot gehat a kontakt dortn,

00:11:16.665 --> 00:11:21.974
m'hot geholfn, m'hot ibergegebn a andere nomen, m'hot fardreyt, m'hot epes getun.

00:11:21.913 --> 00:11:23.985
vi hostu gemakht, vos hot,

00:11:23.985 --> 00:11:25.872
mit vemenen ot di?

00:11:25.018 --> 00:11:25.839
o!

00:11:26.503 --> 00:11:29.804
dortn iz geven a politishe apteylung.

00:11:29.845 --> 00:11:31.864
hobn dortn gearbet

00:11:32.933 --> 00:11:35.509
heftlingen oykhet, arestantn,

00:11:35.785 --> 00:11:38.327
vayl di daytshn hobn tsugenumen tsu der arbet.

00:11:38.788 --> 00:11:42.747
un dortn hot men gedreyt, geshribn, m'hot getun epes.

00:11:43.665 --> 00:11:44.992
mikh aleyn,

00:11:48.458 --> 00:11:52.167
zogt er, "vos heyst, host a pas, du shtamst fun Poyln,

00:11:52.167 --> 00:11:57.868
un m'shraybt dortn ahin dortn vu bist geboyrn gevorn, zey veysn fun gornisht fun dir?"

00:11:58.144 --> 00:11:59.201
farshteyst?

00:11:59.427 --> 00:12:01.631
nu vos zol ikh tu- vos vilstu tun?

00:12:02.346 --> 00:12:04.787
zogt er, ikh veys nisht vos tsu tun, zog ikh,

00:12:04.827 --> 00:12:07.245
bahalt es, leyg es dervayl avek,

00:12:07.245 --> 00:12:08.111
shpet-

00:12:08.691 --> 00:12:14.608
konst dikh nisht forshteln vos far a arbet iz gevezn tsu rateven mentshn.

00:12:16.707 --> 00:12:19.873
m'hot geendert di nemen, un azoy vayter,

00:12:20.419 --> 00:12:21.546
a sakh tsu redn.

00:12:21.546 --> 00:12:24.649
ikh a bikhele kenstu geyn tsu leyenen vegn dem.

00:12:24.199 --> 00:12:28.597
konst zog zog mir yetst, darfst darfst nisht shraybn, konst,

00:12:29.920 --> 00:12:41.254
shoyn. dos iz gevezn, nakher iz m- hot men dem tsentn dem eleftn april finef un fertsik, di amerikaner armey iz gegebn a kum arayn keyn Bukhnvald,

00:12:41.395 --> 00:12:43.599
un m'iz gevorn fraye mentshn.

00:12:44.550 --> 00:12:45.610
for dos.

00:12:45.610 --> 00:12:49.185
mit vemenen hostu gearbet in di untererdishe?

00:12:50.322 --> 00:12:52.155
konst gedenken a nomen?

00:12:52.262 --> 00:12:53.656
ho ho ho.

00:12:55.080 --> 00:12:56.896
a yam mit nemen.

00:12:57.949 --> 00:12:58.736
nu.

00:12:58.843 --> 00:13:05.084
mit a Rovinskin, a Zhvaronoski, freg dikh gornisht, a yam, mit a Dombrovski,

00:13:05.084 --> 00:13:10.464
vayl ikh hob nor mitgearbet mit di polyakn, hot men gehat UNK, ikh bin dokh geven a polyak.

00:13:10.487 --> 00:13:11.274
farshteyst?

00:13:11.652 --> 00:13:15.375
zey hobn yetst nisht geveysn az gevisn az du bist

00:13:15.432 --> 00:13:16.995
n- bist a yid?

00:13:16.545 --> 00:13:18.969
a sakh hobn gevust a sakh nisht.

00:13:19.752 --> 00:13:21.416
efsher hobn zey gevust

00:13:22.148 --> 00:13:23.357
ikh veys nisht.

00:13:26.923 --> 00:13:28.413
un du host nisht

00:13:28.413 --> 00:13:30.244
far dir

00:13:30.244 --> 00:13:34.156
avekgeloyfn far, zey hobn nisht gemakht far dir?

00:13:36.610 --> 00:13:38.679
in Bukhnvald iz gevezn

00:13:39.765 --> 00:13:44.082
zeyer tolerant, m'hot gut bahandlt di, afilek di S. S.

00:13:44.082 --> 00:13:45.682
hot gut bahandlt di

00:13:46.347 --> 00:13:48.821
di heftlingen, di arestantn.

00:13:49.114 --> 00:13:53.040
vayl zey hobn zey badrofn tsu di arbet, gemakht farshidene arbetn,

00:13:54.413 --> 00:14:00.077
un shpeter, in yor toyznt nayn hundert fir un fertsik, un oygust,

00:14:00.319 --> 00:14:04.717
hobn di amerikaner bombardirt Bukhnvald,

00:14:07.778 --> 00:14:11.805
un di ale dokumentn zenen gevorn farbrent,

00:14:13.532 --> 00:14:16.361
hoy hob ikh gezogt, ikh vel shoyn iberlebn.

00:14:17.599 --> 00:14:18.690
herst?

00:14:17.650 --> 00:14:22.639
a sakh mentshn hobn geshtorbn in Bukhnvald ven du host geven dortn?

00:14:21.649 --> 00:14:33.742
yo, a sakh zenen keseyder geshtorbn, fun hunger, fun noyt, un azoy vayter. a sakh hobn zey umgebrengt, di daytshn, farnikhtet, zey hobn gehat gaz-kamern dortn,

00:14:23.674 --> 00:14:25.136
vos iz geshen?

00:14:33.799 --> 00:14:35.548
nor nokh dem

00:14:35.622 --> 00:14:40.698
vi der in oygust fir un fertsik hobn di amerikaner bombardirt,

00:14:40.698 --> 00:14:44.402
Bukhnvald iz gevorn farnikhtet

00:14:44.402 --> 00:14:48.289
der gantser azoy-gerufener arkhiv

00:14:48.598 --> 00:14:50.246
fun dokumentn

00:14:50.826 --> 00:14:53.978
un zey hobn nisht gevust ver vu iz vos,

00:14:53.978 --> 00:14:56.018
zog ikh vel ikh shoyn blaybn lebn.

00:14:57.103 --> 00:15:01.282
s'geven far dir zeyer shver in Bukhnvald?

00:15:01.018 --> 00:15:02.885
neyn, ikh hob gehat gut.

00:15:03.988 --> 00:15:05.416
un andere mentshn?

00:15:06.165 --> 00:15:10.158
m'iz adurkh, m'hot m'iz adurkhgekumen, avade iz men,

00:15:10.587 --> 00:15:13.635
gehungert spetsyel hot men nisht, oder,

00:15:15.328 --> 00:15:18.885
di GUARDS hobn, di S.S. iz nisht geven

00:15:18.885 --> 00:15:20.553
shver fun dir?

00:15:20.391 --> 00:15:21.228
neyn.

00:15:22.956 --> 00:15:25.447
un di arbet, nisht geven,

00:15:25.386 --> 00:15:27.860
nisht geven keyn tsu shvere, neyn.

00:15:29.470 --> 00:15:31.407
fabrikn, farshteyst?

00:15:31.407 --> 00:15:36.022
m'hot nisht gehat gegrobn dortn oyf erd un azoy vayter vi in Aushvits,

00:15:36.022 --> 00:15:37.614
gemakht shoseyen.

00:15:37.924 --> 00:15:39.963
du host gearbet mit yidn?

00:15:39.963 --> 00:15:42.373
ober bloyz mit polyakn?

00:15:42.649 --> 00:15:49.038
s'geven yidn oykhet, shnayders tsvey dray, m'hot zikh nokh gekont fun Varshe.

00:15:51.036 --> 00:15:55.789
zey zenen tsurikgeforn nakher keyn Frankraykh un azoy vayter, eyner iz geforn keyn Shvedn,

00:15:56.672 --> 00:15:58.910
a por yidn hobn gearbet UNK.

00:16:00.958 --> 00:16:03.399
du meynst az du host gelebt

00:16:03.591 --> 00:16:09.170
far du host gehat papirn vos hobn gezogt az du bist nisht a yi-

00:16:07.860 --> 00:16:12.427
yo, g- goyishke papirn, polyakish, poylishe papirn.

00:16:13.092 --> 00:16:15.516
a dank dem bin ikh geblibn lebn.

00:16:19.926 --> 00:16:23.230
du host geven a tsayt ven du host nisht

00:16:23.230 --> 00:16:24.943
host farloyrn

00:16:24.943 --> 00:16:29.302
HOPE, ven du host gemeynt az du vel nisht lebn?

00:16:30.760 --> 00:16:31.733
her,

00:16:33.190 --> 00:16:36.795
mentshn hobn nisht geklert di zakhn, geven a tsayt,

00:16:36.936 --> 00:16:39.934
m'hot gekemft m'zol blaybn lebn.

00:16:41.323 --> 00:16:42.527
farshteyst?

00:16:42.527 --> 00:16:43.343
o!

00:16:45.660 --> 00:16:48.928
du ho- du konst gedenken

00:16:49.137 --> 00:16:57.146
un oysergeveynlekhe gesheenish in Bukhnvald ven du host ho- geholfn emetser?

00:16:58.401 --> 00:17:02.074
vos kon dortn zayn oysergeveynlekhe gesheenishn?

00:17:05.505 --> 00:17:09.026
in a tfise, bist gegangen in der fri tsu der arbet,

00:17:09.285 --> 00:17:14.139
gearbet a gantsn tog, host gekrign a bisl esn, dos iz alts gevezn.

00:17:15.292 --> 00:17:18.813
du host gezogt ah frier az du host geholfn mentshn.

00:17:18.651 --> 00:17:20.096
m'hot geholfn.

00:17:20.136 --> 00:17:21.668
kinder oykhet?

00:17:21.621 --> 00:17:22.560
vos?

00:17:21.668 --> 00:17:23.741
kinder oykhet?

00:17:22.836 --> 00:17:23.572
neyn.

00:17:23.898 --> 00:17:25.562
kinder nisht gevezn.

00:17:29.751 --> 00:17:32.735
vu hostu gearbet in

00:17:33.012 --> 00:17:35.194
Bukhnvald, bloyz?

00:17:34.480 --> 00:17:35.773
shnayderay.

00:17:42.867 --> 00:17:46.421
vu, du host nisht geholfn mentshn vos

00:17:47.271 --> 00:17:50.420
vos hobn gekumen, s'geven DIF-

00:17:50.275 --> 00:17:55.837
s'gekumen mentshn, oyb s'geven bakante mentshn hot men zey geholfn,

00:17:56.164 --> 00:18:01.980
m'hot zey gevizn, m'hot zey arayngefirt gegebn arbet, m'hot geholfn kegnzaytik.

00:18:02.205 --> 00:18:05.219
in Bukhnvald hot men zikh zeyer shtark geholfn.

00:18:05.344 --> 00:18:06.856
eyner dem andern.

00:18:06.930 --> 00:18:11.463
nor er hot gemuzt zayn farbindn mit a natsyonalistishe grupe.

00:18:11.858 --> 00:18:13.483
polyakn hobn geholfn.

00:18:13.483 --> 00:18:16.492
yidn zenen a mol gevezn,

00:18:17.899 --> 00:18:26.164
daytshe yidn hot men a mol gebrengt in akht un draysikstn yor keyn Bukhnvald. tsvontsik toyznt yidn. geblibn zenen efsher

00:18:26.164 --> 00:18:27.565
fuftsik yidn.

00:18:27.565 --> 00:18:29.503
ale hot men oysgeharget.

00:18:29.509 --> 00:18:35.088
un di fuftsik yidn zenen geven in farshidene amtn un azoy vayter, geblibn lebn.

00:18:35.382 --> 00:18:37.671
fun tsvontsik toyznt yidn.

00:18:38.487 --> 00:18:39.848
in Bukhnvald.

00:18:40.933 --> 00:18:44.656
vayl der Bukhnvald iz antshtanen in akht un draysikstn yor.

00:18:44.983 --> 00:18:46.107
der lager.

00:18:48.882 --> 00:18:53.027
kum nor, lomir makhn an iberrays, neyn du vilst nisht? makh!

00:18:53.083 --> 00:18:54.714
ikh hob shoyn nisht keyn koyekh

00:18:54.889 --> 00:18:56.486
tsu redn azoy fil.

00:18:56.391 --> 00:18:58.843
a bisl mer, a bisl.

00:18:57.488 --> 00:18:59.777
nu, zog mir vosh, ikh freg dikh.

00:19:00.019 --> 00:19:04.243
du host geshribn shpeter fun vos iz geshen mit

00:19:04.243 --> 00:19:05.868
mit di- dayn lebn.

00:19:05.993 --> 00:19:07.539
nu, ikh hob geshribn.

00:19:09.216 --> 00:19:11.943
ikh hob geshribn in yidish, ikh hob geshribn in Poylish.

00:19:12.777 --> 00:19:14.678
ven du host geshribn,

00:19:15.915 --> 00:19:17.557
vos hostu geshribn,

00:19:17.557 --> 00:19:18.643
fun vos?

00:19:18.379 --> 00:19:21.765
vos heyst vos ikh hob geshribn? vos ikh hob gedenkt hob ikh geshribn.

00:19:22.328 --> 00:19:24.077
on dokumentn.

00:19:24.893 --> 00:19:28.059
do iz geven der dokument un ikh hob geshribn.

00:19:30.360 --> 00:19:31.687
v- du host gezogt

00:19:31.761 --> 00:19:38.792
far finef fir un fertsik ven di AMERICAN hot bombardirt, vos iz geshen fun

00:19:36.672 --> 00:19:37.476
yo.

00:19:39.388 --> 00:19:43.468
f- fir un fertsik biz april finef un fertsik?

00:19:43.468 --> 00:19:44.478
vos hot gemakht?

00:19:44.147 --> 00:19:48.005
nu shoyn, in dem lager iz shoyn geven a rizn balagan,

00:19:48.383 --> 00:19:49.339
dos heyst

00:19:49.851 --> 00:19:54.556
mentshn hobn shoyn nisht gearbet, arumgelofn, a sakh zenen antlofn,

00:19:54.556 --> 00:19:55.970
a sakh mentshn,

00:19:57.563 --> 00:20:06.011
biz dem ershtn april, bizn eleftn april, in tsentn tsi in eleftn april, iz ongekumen di amerikaner armeyen, frayheyt gemakht.

00:20:05.933 --> 00:20:07.429
vos iz geshen?

00:20:07.283 --> 00:20:09.926
vos heyst? zey hobn bakemft di doytshn.

00:20:10.725 --> 00:20:12.423
vos hostu gezen?

00:20:12.379 --> 00:20:17.767
gornisht gezen, ikh hob nor gezen onkumen amerikaner militer.

00:20:17.767 --> 00:20:19.663
arayngekumen in lager.

00:20:20.327 --> 00:20:21.682
du host geveyst,

00:20:21.682 --> 00:20:25.468
vemen ho- vemenen fun di amerikanisher iz geven?

00:20:25.508 --> 00:20:26.531
di di,

00:20:26.166 --> 00:20:32.910
ikh veys nor eyn nomen, general Patn, hot er gefirt mit di aktsye, bafrayen Bukhnvald.

00:20:33.287 --> 00:20:35.373
un du host im gezen?

00:20:35.278 --> 00:20:36.639
avade!

00:20:37.017 --> 00:20:39.188
ikh hobn afile gegebn di hant oykhet.

00:20:40.476 --> 00:20:44.925
un vos hot di amerikanisher getun ven zey hobn gekumen?

00:20:43.986 --> 00:20:44.942
nu!

00:20:46.264 --> 00:20:48.148
iz di ershte zakh,

00:20:49.082 --> 00:20:52.327
hobn zey tsunoyfgenumen ale

00:20:52.327 --> 00:20:54.999
heftlingen vos hobn gelebt.

00:20:57.267 --> 00:21:01.108
nor s'geven a groyser tsol kranke in di shpiteler,

00:21:02.717 --> 00:21:04.938
un shtel dikh for

00:21:06.953 --> 00:21:10.001
s'geven efsher zibetsn toyznt bafr-

00:21:10.024 --> 00:21:11.975
lebedike mentshn,

00:21:12.437 --> 00:21:16.768
in a sheynem moment hot men gegebn a breng aroys dos yingele,

00:21:17.415 --> 00:21:21.071
im hot es oykhet gevizn, er iz geblibn lebn.

00:21:21.617 --> 00:21:25.205
un a rebe fun di amerikaner armey

00:21:26.427 --> 00:21:28.355
iz tsu tsu dem yingele,

00:21:28.355 --> 00:21:32.360
er hot gezogt kadesh un dos yingele hot nokhgezogt.

00:21:33.463 --> 00:21:34.959
zog mir fun

00:21:34.982 --> 00:21:36.258
dos yingele.

00:21:37.142 --> 00:21:39.245
di historye fun dos yingele.

00:21:39.083 --> 00:21:42.092
leyn iber, dos iz dortn do, ikh hob nisht keyn koye-

00:21:42.092 --> 00:21:43.734
leyen iber dortn.

00:21:44.365 --> 00:21:47.886
du konst mir nisht zogn a bisl fun vos iz geshen?

00:21:46.272 --> 00:21:47.880
vos zol ikh dir zogn?

00:21:47.880 --> 00:21:50.383
a yid fun Aushvits

00:21:50.406 --> 00:21:56.407
vayl dos iz fun ge- Aushvits fun likvidirt Aushvits hot men di mentshn gebrengt keyn Bukhnvald.

00:21:57.831 --> 00:22:02.550
iz er gegangen, geforn un gehat a kleyn valizkele.

00:22:03.062 --> 00:22:05.722
dortn iz gelign a yidish kind.

00:22:06.775 --> 00:22:11.612
er hot e- biz m'hot es opgeratvet, a gantse geshikhte dortn bashribn,

00:22:13.103 --> 00:22:16.539
un shpeter ven der gantser lager iz aroys,

00:22:16.900 --> 00:22:19.307
un di ofitsere hobn bagrist,

00:22:19.313 --> 00:22:23.306
un m'hot gebrengt dos kind, aroysgebrengt fun unter der erd,

00:22:23.363 --> 00:22:26.749
iz tsu dortn a rebe, in di amerikaner armey,

00:22:26.299 --> 00:22:32.042
vos iz geshen mit di yingele ven di ven di m- man hot gekumen mit di valizkele,

00:22:32.042 --> 00:22:33.887
vos iz ge- geshen?

00:22:32.830 --> 00:22:33.887
o!

00:22:34.585 --> 00:22:36.148
m'hot, kh'zog ikh dir,

00:22:36.306 --> 00:22:38.173
m'hot es bald bahaltn.

00:22:38.280 --> 00:22:45.513
un der mentsh vos hot gebrengt dos kind hot genumen arumzukhn, vu iz es? hot men gezogt, hob nisht keyn moyre, es lebt, s'do.

00:22:46.127 --> 00:22:51.836
farshteyst, er iz gekumen un im hot men dortn genumen in di ve- er zol zikh opvashn un azoy vayter,

00:22:51.836 --> 00:22:53.293
geblibn in

00:22:53.569 --> 00:22:55.683
un m'hot opgeratevet dos kind,

00:22:55.683 --> 00:23:02.577
un nakher iz dos kind, shtel dikh for, nisht mer un nisht vintsiker, forgeshtelt far zibetsn toyznt mentshn,

00:23:02.577 --> 00:23:04.329
a geratevet kind,

00:23:03.542 --> 00:23:07.130
vi lang hostu geratevet mit di kind?

00:23:07.170 --> 00:23:08.801
hot gedoyert a tsen teg.

00:23:09.718 --> 00:23:10.609
tsen teg.

00:23:10.609 --> 00:23:13.374
un vos hostu getun mit di kind?

00:23:13.566 --> 00:23:15.467
vi hostu gerava-

00:23:15.372 --> 00:23:17.998
ven dos kind iz gevorn gerap- -evet,

00:23:18.207 --> 00:23:22.084
der amerikaner rebe hot gezogt mit es kadesh,

00:23:22.084 --> 00:23:24.410
ikh veys nisht tsi dos kind hot gut nokhgezogt,

00:23:25.935 --> 00:23:29.641
hot men dos kind bald avekgefirt keyn Frankraykh.

00:23:29.698 --> 00:23:33.775
nakher keyn Shveytsarye. vos iz gevorn vayter veys ikh nisht.

00:23:34.727 --> 00:23:37.027
un vi alt iz gev- di kind geven?

00:23:36.955 --> 00:23:37.944
vos?

00:23:37.027 --> 00:23:39.446
vi alt hot di kind?

00:23:38.980 --> 00:23:41.370
dos kind? dray un a halb yor.

00:23:42.726 --> 00:23:45.119
un bloyz tsen teg du host,

00:23:45.004 --> 00:23:45.929
yo.

00:23:45.119 --> 00:23:47.006
geratevet?

00:23:45.929 --> 00:23:48.795
yo, er iz nisht lang geven in ahm Bukhnvald.

00:23:49.729 --> 00:23:54.802
vayl der hot im gefirt fun Aushvits keyn Bukhnvald in a kleyn valizkele.

00:23:55.500 --> 00:23:58.599
vi dos kind hot oysgehaltn, vunder!

00:24:00.023 --> 00:24:01.589
un er voynt yetst?

00:24:01.103 --> 00:24:02.109
vos?

00:24:01.589 --> 00:24:03.124
er voynt yetst?

00:24:03.043 --> 00:24:05.585
Shveytsarye, in SHVITZERLAND.

00:24:05.473 --> 00:24:06.643
du host im gezen?

00:24:06.604 --> 00:24:07.458
neyn.

00:24:07.498 --> 00:24:10.128
er iz do geven tsvey mol, ikh hob im nisht gezen.

00:24:10.128 --> 00:24:12.285
er hot epes familye do, veys.

00:24:14.029 --> 00:24:16.520
ven di, vos iz geshen

00:24:17.539 --> 00:24:22.258
AFTER THE amerikanisher hobn arayngekumen, vos iz geshen tsu dir?

00:24:22.197 --> 00:24:24.182
ikh tsurikgeforn keyn Poyln.

00:24:26.685 --> 00:24:28.771
STRAIGHT AWAY? neyn.

00:24:28.761 --> 00:24:35.052
STRAIGHT AWAY. farshidene vegn, mit di ban, mit di COLOURS, mit a kar un azoy vayter,

00:24:35.052 --> 00:24:37.158
m'iz ongekumen tsurik keyn Poyln.

00:24:36.861 --> 00:24:39.437
ven hostu ge- tsurikgekumen tsu POLAND?

00:24:39.679 --> 00:24:42.120
ven ikh bin gekumen keyn Poyln,

00:24:42.548 --> 00:24:45.866
hob ikh keynem fun der familye nisht getrofn,

00:24:46.581 --> 00:24:50.085
nor ikh bin gevoyer gevorn eyn shvester

00:24:50.091 --> 00:24:51.722
hot zikh geratevet,

00:24:53.905 --> 00:24:55.991
hot gevoynt in Vrodslav,

00:24:56.588 --> 00:24:58.438
ikh hob ir oysgefunen.

00:24:58.123 --> 00:24:59.399
vi azoy?

00:25:00.081 --> 00:25:03.804
durkh bakante, durkh polyakn, azoy vayter, oysgefunen,

00:25:03.895 --> 00:25:06.352
un nakher di shvester mayne

00:25:07.000 --> 00:25:08.186
iz n-

00:25:08.186 --> 00:25:10.943
avek keyn Yisroel mitn man,

00:25:11.370 --> 00:25:13.068
un dortn,

00:25:13.581 --> 00:25:17.147
zi iz shoyn geshtorbn di shvester in Yisroel, der man,

00:25:17.147 --> 00:25:19.683
un zey hobn a zun in Yisroel.

00:25:20.061 --> 00:25:22.350
un m'iz in farbindung un azoy vayter.

00:25:23.115 --> 00:25:27.651
ven hostu tsurikgekumen tsu POLAND?

00:25:27.651 --> 00:25:28.424
ven?

00:25:28.785 --> 00:25:33.014
ikh bin tsurik in Poyln in finef un fertsikstn yor,

00:25:33.780 --> 00:25:40.001
dem in tsen- punkt vi di milkhome hot zikh farendikt, in tsentn may.

00:25:40.108 --> 00:25:41.992
akhte may, tsente.

00:25:42.032 --> 00:25:43.983
tsurikgekumen keyn Poyln.

00:25:44.496 --> 00:25:47.932
AND vu in Poylnd hostu gevoynt?

00:25:48.985 --> 00:25:51.375
azoy vi ikh bin ge- tsurikgekumen,

00:25:53.592 --> 00:25:58.277
iz dos ershte gegangen in di voynung vu ikh hob gevoynt.

00:25:59.076 --> 00:26:03.272
un shtel dir for s'nisht geven bombardirt gornisht,

00:26:04.965 --> 00:26:15.944
un ikh bin aroyf oyfn tsveytn shtok un geklapt in di tir hot mir a polyak geefnt di tir, zog ikh dos iz mayn voynung, UNK, hot mikh avekgevorfn,

00:26:17.031 --> 00:26:19.331
avek! zogt er, s'nisht dayn!

00:26:19.331 --> 00:26:21.440
un m'hot mir tsugenumen di voynung.

00:26:21.440 --> 00:26:23.656
bin ikh gegangen in der partey,

00:26:24.523 --> 00:26:26.441
un gezogt, vos iz do geshen?

00:26:27.747 --> 00:26:32.398
m'hot mir tsugenumen di voynung, m'lozt mir nisht a- oy, zogn zey, vos kon men tun?

00:26:34.463 --> 00:26:39.941
shtel dir for zog ikh dir, vu vel ikh nekhtikn, zogt er, m'vet dir gebn a

00:26:41.415 --> 00:26:44.058
a bilet un du vest geyn

00:26:44.301 --> 00:26:46.607
dortn in dem hotel.

00:26:47.727 --> 00:26:50.218
nisht gehat keyn breyre, bin ikh gegangen.

00:26:51.152 --> 00:26:53.283
ongekumen eleve bay nakht,

00:26:53.283 --> 00:26:55.432
shteyt dortn a soldat,

00:26:55.860 --> 00:26:57.086
a zelner,

00:26:57.328 --> 00:27:01.861
vi heyst du? zog ikh, ikh hob do a kvitl ikh zol do nakhtikn. hot er mir aroyfgelozt.

00:27:01.902 --> 00:27:03.822
shoyn geven nokh eleve bay nakht.

00:27:03.822 --> 00:27:06.266
un ikh klap in di tir un klap,

00:27:07.707 --> 00:27:10.046
in dem her ikh a gevald,

00:27:10.491 --> 00:27:14.124
"vos iz dos far a bandit, klapt eleve bay nakht,!"

00:27:14.124 --> 00:27:17.263
zog ikh, Yadzhele, shray nisht, oyf poylish,

00:27:17.263 --> 00:27:18.753
UNK.

00:27:18.793 --> 00:27:21.971
dos iz geven mayns a bakante hot geshrign dort.

00:27:21.971 --> 00:27:25.886
yetst geefnt di tir un azoy arumet bin ikh arayngekumen

00:27:25.886 --> 00:27:27.630
tsurik tsvishn mentshn.

00:27:28.868 --> 00:27:30.417
vos hostu gemakht

00:27:30.417 --> 00:27:32.811
in WARSAW? vos hostu getun?

00:27:33.660 --> 00:27:35.510
oyfn tsveytn tog,

00:27:35.955 --> 00:27:37.943
zogt zi, gey arbetn!

00:27:37.943 --> 00:27:40.387
di bakante vayl er hot mir arayngelozt.

00:27:40.731 --> 00:27:42.260
bin ikh gegangen

00:27:42.587 --> 00:27:44.977
tsu a froy velkhe hot geheysn

00:27:45.085 --> 00:27:47.812
Zosha Gomulkova.

00:27:49.185 --> 00:27:55.518
di froy fun general ⟨sekretar⟩ fun der partey, vayl ikh hob ir gekont fun far der milkhome.

00:27:55.518 --> 00:27:57.718
zog ikh, ikh bin gekumen fun lager,

00:27:59.732 --> 00:28:03.624
m'vet dikh makhn, zogt zi, far an ofitsir fun der politsey.

00:28:03.681 --> 00:28:05.497
zog ikh, "Zoshkele,

00:28:05.908 --> 00:28:15.993
hak mir nisht in kop arayn, ikh hob genug di politsey far di milkhome, in tsayt fun di okupatsye, un du geyst mikh makhn far a politsyant?" zogt zi, "nu vos den zol ikh makhn dikh?"

00:28:16.050 --> 00:28:21.410
zog ikh, "du veyst dokh vos far a fakh ikh hob." "oy," zogt zi, "a vunderbarer gedank!

00:28:21.450 --> 00:28:23.300
makh a varshtat!

00:28:23.509 --> 00:28:27.522
a shnayder-varshtat in tsentral-komitet,

00:28:27.522 --> 00:28:31.451
un du vest farrikhtn di antsiger fun di khaveyrim."

00:28:32.200 --> 00:28:35.636
un ikh, tsvey yor hob ikh gefirt azan varshtat.

00:28:36.402 --> 00:28:38.573
in tsentral-komitet.

00:28:39.270 --> 00:28:41.511
du host nisht gefunen andere

00:28:41.511 --> 00:28:43.264
mentshn vos hobn gevoynt

00:28:43.388 --> 00:28:47.381
a bisl gefunen azoy vayter, ikh gedenk nisht di nemen.

00:28:43.523 --> 00:28:44.749
in Varshe?

00:28:47.944 --> 00:28:49.794
azoy, er redt tsu dir.

00:28:51.218 --> 00:28:53.085
m'vet vay- yetst

00:28:53.142 --> 00:28:54.570
oystoyshn

00:28:54.576 --> 00:28:57.239
neyn, makh a ps- ikh hob shoyn nisht keyn koyekh tsu redn.

00:28:54.593 --> 00:28:55.836
TAPE.
